Class HomogeneousExpression<T extends SymbolicObject>

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BooleanPrimitive, CommonReferenceExpression, CommonSymbolicConstant, CompoundBooleanExpression, HerbrandExpression, NTConstant, NTMonic, NTMonomial, NTPolynomial, NTPrimitivePower, NTRationalExpression, NumericPrimitive, One

    public class HomogeneousExpression<T extends SymbolicObject>
extends CommonSymbolicObject
implements SymbolicExpression
    Implementation of SymbolicExpression in which every argument belongs to some type T which extends SymbolicObject.
